This is a quick note to confirm your GradConnect password was just changed.

If you made this change, no action is needed. As a precaution, you've been signed out of all other devices.

If you didn't change your password, your account may be compromised. Reset your password immediately at https://gradconnect.ng/forgot-password and contact us at support@gradconnect.ng.

Best regards,
The GradConnect Team
